攔住那些孩子！
Stop those children!

1248
01:36:10,251 --> 01:36:14,254
攔住孩子！
Stop those children!

1249
01:36:31,437 --> 01:36:35,314
跟我來，親愛的。我幫你藏起來
Come with me, my dears. Granny'll hide you!

1250
01:36:52,874 --> 01:36:56,544
這兒，這兒，等一下 放開她，把我的姐姐放開！
Here, here, half a mo.
Leave her alone! Leave my sister alone!

1251
