You're filthy!
Oh, perhaps a smudge or two.

1255
01:37:10,975 --> 01:37:13,143
碰巧今天我是個掃煙囪的人
It so happens that today I'm a chimney sweep.

1256
01:37:13,394 --> 01:37:15,603
哦，伯特，我們嚇得要命
Oh, Bert, we're so frightened.

1257
01:37:15,855 --> 01:37:17,981
