Now, now, don't take on so.

1258
01:37:18,231 --> 01:37:21,024
伯特會向你們的父親那樣照顧好你們的
Bert'll take care of you like I was your own father.

1259
01:37:21,276 --> 01:37:23,318
誰在追你們？ 我們的父親……
Now, who's after you?
Father is.

1260
01:37:23,570 --> 01:37:26,488
什麼？ 他帶我們去他的銀行參觀
What?
He brought us to see his bank.

1261
01:37:26,739 --> 01:37:29,825
我不知道我們做了什麼，但一定是非常糟糕的事情
I don't know what we did, but it must've been something dreadful.

1262
01:37:30,076 --> 01:37:33,203
