You know, begging your pardon...

1272
01:37:58,102 --> 01:38:01,146
我很同情你們的父親
but the one my heart goes out to is your father.

1273
01:38:01,397 --> 01:38:05,233
他在那個冷酷的，無情的銀行中日復一日地……
There he is in that cold, heartless bank day after day...

1274
01:38:05,483 --> 01:38:09,068
被一大堆冰冷的，無感情的金錢所包圍
hemmed in by mounds of cold, heartless money.

1275
01:38:09,321 --> 01:38:10,989
我不喜歡看到任何生命被關在籠中
I don't like to see any living thing caged up.

1276
01:38:11,239 --> 01:38:13,741
父親被關在籠子裏了？
Father in a cage?

1277
01:38:13,992 --> 01:38:16,868
