掃帚用來掃煙囪，用刷子來通煙道
A broom for the shaft and a brush for the flue

1339
01:42:01,997 --> 01:42:04,999
這裏很黑很暗
Oh, it's awfully dark and gloomy up there.

1340
01:42:05,250 --> 01:42:08,002
現在，你將知道你的看法是錯誤的
There now. You see how wrong people can be?

1341
01:42:08,253 --> 01:42:13,091
這兒是通向你所謂魔法世界的一條通道
That there is what you might call a doorway to a place of enchantment.

1342
01:42:13,342 --> 01:42:18,012
在上面煙霧如巨浪般翻滾，捲曲
Up where the smoke is all billowed and curled

1343
01:42:18,263 --> 01:42:20,932
在星星和地面之間
'Tween pavement and stars

1344
01:42:21,182 --> 01:42:25,102
是掃煙囪人的世界
Is the chimney sweep world

1345
01:42:25,103 --> 01:42:27,604
這裏幾乎沒有白天
When there's hardly no day

1346
01:42:27,856 --> 01:42:30,691
也幾乎沒有黑夜
Nor hardly no night

1347
01:42:30,942 --> 01:42:34,945
所有的事物一半在陰影裏
There's things half in shadow

1348
01:42:35,195 --> 01:42:38,239
一半在光線下
And halfway in light

1349
01:42:38,490 --> 01:42:43,869
站在倫敦的屋頂
On the rooftops of London

1350
01:42:44,120 --> 01:42:47,206
視野真開闊
Coo, what a sight.

1351
01:42:47,457 --> 01:42:49,749
我真希望我們能到上面去
I do wish we could go up there.

1352
01:42:50,001 --> 01:42:52,044
我也是！我喜歡煙囪
So do I! I like chimneys.

1353
01:42:52,295 --> 01:42:57,091
非常正確！煙囪是一件完美的東西
Oh, rightly so! A chimney is a wondrous thing.

1354
01:42:57,342 --> 01:42:59,593
她高高地建在屋頂上
She's built tall right up there on the roof.

1355
01:42:59,843 --> 01:43:03,096
當風向正確的時候，風吹過她的頂端
When the wind is just right, it blows across her top...

1356
