1524
02:00:01,595 --> 02:00:03,887
慫恿你帶孩子們出門遠足？ 是的
Tricked you into taking the children on an outing?
Yes.

1525
02:00:04,138 --> 02:00:05,764
真無恥！
Outrageous!

1526
02:00:06,015 --> 02:00:11,602
一個男人有許多重要的事情要去做。真可恥！
A man with all the important things you have to do. Shameful!

1527
02:00:11,689 --> 02:00:15,274
你是一個有身份的男人
You're a man of high position.

1528
02:00:15,525 --> 02:00:18,360
受同齡人的尊敬
Esteemed by your peers.

1529
02:00:18,610 --> 02:00:21,946
當你的孩子們哭泣的時候
And when your little tykes are cryin'

1530
02:00:22,197 --> 02:00:26,074
你沒有時間去擦乾他們的眼淚
You haven't time to dry their tears

1531
02:00:26,326 --> 02:00:30,078
瞧瞧他們感激地小臉蛋
And see them grateful little faces

1532
02:00:30,331 --> 02:00:33,709
衝著你微笑
Smilin' up at you

1533
02:00:33,959 --> 02:00:36,002
因為他們的爸爸
Because their dad

1534
02:00:36,253 --> 02:00:40,714
總是知道什麼是應該做的
He always knows just what to do

1535
02:00:40,965 --> 02:00:44,968
呃，我的意思是，瞧，我不認為我…… 就像你說的，老爸
Well, I mean, look, I, I don't think I ca...
Like you say, guv'nor.

1536
02:00:45,220 --> 02:00:49,557
你不得不在石磨上
You've got to grind, grind, grind

1537
02:00:49,808 --> 02:00:53,060
不停地磨呀磨呀磨
At that grindstone

1538
02:00:53,310 --> 02:00:55,770
雖然童年時光
Though childhood slips

1539
02:00:56,021 --> 02:01:01,109
就像沙子穿過沙漏
Like sand through a sieve

1540
02:01:01,484 --> 02:01:06,155
很快他們就長大
And all too soon they've up and grown

1541
02:01:06,406 --> 02:01:10,867
接著他們就離你而去
And then they've flown

1542
02:01:11,119 --> 02:01:13,579
那時你再後悔
And it's too late

1543
02:01:13,830 --> 02:01:19,709
就太遲了
For you to give

1544
02:01:21,170 --> 02:01:26,300
就好像一湯匙糖
Just that spoonful of sugar

1545
02:01:26,550 --> 02:01:30,594
能夠幫助把藥服下
To help the medicine go down

1546
02:01:30,846 --> 02:01:34,932
甜藥
The medicine go down

1547
02:01:35,183 --> 02:01:38,102
好入口
Medicine go down

1548
02:01:38,353 --> 02:01:43,106
好了，再見，老爸，很抱歉給你惹了這麼多麻煩
Well, goodbye, guv'nor. Sorry to have troubled you.

1549
02:01:54,868 --> 02:01:57,119
父親？
Father?

1550
02:01:57,370 --> 02:01:59,954
我們對兩便士的事情非常抱歉
We're sorry about the tuppence.

1551
02:02:00,206 --> 02:02:05,043
我們不知道那會引起這麼大的麻煩
We didn't know it would cause you so much trouble.

1552
02:02:10,174 --> 02:02:14,844
父親，給你兩便士
Here, Father, you can have the tuppence.

1553
02:02:26,898 --> 02:02:31,319
這樣能平息所有的風波嗎？
Will that make everything all right?

1554
02:02:31,569 --> 02:02:35,572
謝謝
Thank you.

1555
02:05:25,483 --> 02:05:29,235
進來!
Come in!

1556
02:05:36,618 --> 02:05:39,745
把帽子脫掉，班克斯
Take your hat off, Banks.

1557
02:05:52,759 --> 02:05:56,595
晚上好，先生們
Good evening, gentlemen.

1558
02:05:58,097 --> 02:05:59,889
很好，繼續
Well, get on with it. Go on.

1559
02:06:00,140 --> 02:06:03,892
是，父親
Uh, yes, Father.

1560
02:06:05,812 --> 02:06:09,688
在1773年，這家銀行的一位職員……
In 1773, an official of this bank...

1561
02:06:09,942 --> 02:06:12,234
愚蠢地將一大筆錢借給
unwisely loaned a large sum of money...

1562
02:06:12,485 --> 02:06:16,571
往北美殖民地海運茶葉的貿易
to finance a shipment of tea to the American colonies.

1563
02:06:16,821 --> 02:06:20,533
知道後來發生了什麼事？ 是的，先生，我想我知道
Do you know what happened?
Yes, sir. Yes, I think I do.

1564
02:06:20,785 --> 02:06:22,660
當船停泊在波士頓港的時候
Uh, uh, as the ship lay in Boston Harbor...

1565
02:06:22,912 --> 02:06:25,413
一群殖民地居民打扮成印第安人
uh, a party of the colonists dressed as red Indians...

1566
02:06:25,665 --> 02:06:30,542
登上了船，舉止非常粗魯，還將所有的茶葉傾倒到海裏
uh, boarded the vessel, behaved very rudely, and, and threw all the tea overboard.

1567
02:06:30,794 --> 02:06:33,545
導致茶葉味道變質
This made the tea unsuitable for drinking...

1568
02:06:33,797 --> 02:06:38,008
即使是美國人也不願意喝
even for Americans.

1569
02:06:41,345 --> 02:06:45,056
很對。這筆借款成了呆賬
Precisely. The loan was defaulted.

1570
02:06:45,308 --> 02:06:47,851
在這堵牆內的恐慌接踵而至
Panic ensued within these walls.

1571
02:06:48,102 --> 02:06:51,062
銀行發生了擠兌事件！
There was a run on the bank!

1572
02:06:51,313 --> 02:06:53,231
從那時起到現在，先生……
From that time to this, sir...

1573
02:06:53,482 --> 02:06:58,486
這家銀行還沒有發生過一起擠兌事件
there has not been a run on this bank...

1574
02:06:59,529 --> 02:07:01,446
直到今天！
until today!

1575
02:07:01,697 --> 02:07:06,575
一場擠兌事件，先生，起因是你兒子的可恥的行為
A run, sir, caused by the disgraceful conduct of your son.

1576
02:07:06,828 --> 02:07:10,247
對此你否認嗎？ 我不否認，先生
Do you deny it?
I do not deny it, sir.

1577
02:07:10,498 --> 02:07:16,169
我只能情願為我兒子的行為承擔責任
And I shall be only too glad to assume responsibility for my son.

1578
02:07:18,381 --> 02:07:24,010
你還在等什麼？繼續！ 是，是的，父親
What are you waiting for? Get on with it!
Uh, y-yes, Father.

1579
02:07:41,860 --> 02:07:45,697
不，別這樣！ 鎮定！
No, not that!
Steady on.

1580
02:08:04,715 --> 02:08:07,299
好了，班克斯，你還有什麼話要說的嗎？
Well, do you have anything to say, Banks?

1581
02:08:07,551 --> 02:08:11,387
先生，他們說……
Well, sir, they do say that...

1582
02:08:11,639 --> 02:08:17,644
當你無話可說的時候，你就可以說……
when there's nothing to say, all you can say i...

1583
02:08:19,688 --> 02:08:24,233
班克斯，請搞清楚！我問，你還有什麼說的嗎？
Confound it, Banks! I said, do you have anything to say?

1584
02:08:25,901 --> 02:08:28,570
只有一個詞，先生 什麼詞？
Just one word, sir.
Yes?

1585
02:08:28,822 --> 02:08:32,741
超級霹靂快樂得不得了
Supercalifragilistic-expialidocious.

1586
02:08:33,285 --> 02:08:34,243
什麼？
What?

1587
02:08:34,493 --> 02:08:37,328
超級霹靂快樂得不得了
Supercalifragilistic-expialidocious.

1588
02:08:37,579 --> 02:08:42,375
瑪麗?潑平斯是對的。這個詞很特別，確實能讓你感覺好多了！
Mary Poppins was right. It's extraordinary. It does make you feel better!

1589
02:08:42,418 --> 02:08:44,418
你在說什麼？沒有這個詞
What are you talking about, man? There's no such word.

1590
02:08:44,669 --> 02:08:47,921
不，有這個詞。實際上，它是一個完美的詞
Oh, yes. It is a word. A perfectly good word, actually.

1591
02:08:48,173 --> 02:08:49,590
你知道有這樣的事情嗎？
Do you know what there's no such thing as?

1592
02:08:49,841 --> 02:08:53,009
當所有的事情都說過並做過後，發生……
It turns out, with due respect, when all is said and done...

1593
02:08:53,261 --> 02:08:56,096
像你這樣的事情……
that there's no such thing as you!

1594
02:08:56,347 --> 02:08:58,014
主題，先生！注意談話的主題
Impertinence, sir! Speaking of impertinence...

1595
02:08:58,266 --> 02:09:00,600
你想聽一個絕妙的笑話嗎？
would you like to hear a perfectly marvellous joke?

1596
02:09:00,851 --> 02:09:03,352
一個真正的笑話！ 笑話？真正的？
A real snapper!
Joke? Snapper?

1597
02:09:03,604 --> 02:09:06,690
是的，有兩個優秀的年輕人，簡和邁克爾
Yes. There are these two wonderful young people, Jane and Michael.

1598
02:09:06,941 --> 02:09:10,234
有一天他們在街上相遇，簡跟邁克爾說
And they meet one day on the street, and Jane says to Michael...

1599
02:09:10,485 --> 02:09:13,069
我知道一個有一隻木頭假腿的人，名字叫史密斯 （也可理解為：我知道有個人，他有一隻叫做史密斯的木頭假腿）
"I know a man with a wooden leg named Smith."

1600
02:09:13,321 --> 02:09:19,075
邁克爾問，真的？那他的另一隻腿叫什麼？
And Michael says, "Really? What's the name of his other leg?"

1601
02:09:20,078 --> 02:09:22,370
這個人瘋了，叫警衛
The man's gone mad. Call the guard!

1602
02:09:22,621 --> 02:09:25,999
超級霹靂快樂得不得了，我感覺好極了！
Supercalifragilistic-expialidocious. I'm feeling better all the time!

1603
02:09:26,250 --> 02:09:28,209
班克斯，不准你打擊我的父親！
Banks, don't you dare strike my father!

1604
02:09:28,461 --> 02:09:30,753
這是那兩便士 這是命中注定的，絕妙的
There's the tuppence. The wonderful, fateful...

1605
02:09:31,005 --> 02:09:33,880
超級霹靂快樂得不得了 的兩便士
supercalifragilistic-expialidocious tuppence.

1606
02:09:34,133 --> 02:09:37,051
好好保護它，再見！ 班克斯，你要去哪兒？
Guard it well. Goodbye!
Banks, where are you going?

1607
02:09:37,303 --> 02:09:40,054
我不知道 也許跳進馬路上的粉筆畫裏
I don't know. I might pop through a chalk pavement picture,

1608
02:09:40,306 --> 02:09:41,723
去鄉下遠足
and go for an outing in the country.

1609
02:09:41,973 --> 02:09:45,225
或者騎著一匹旋轉木馬，贏得賽馬比賽
Or I might seize a horse off a merry-go-round, and win the Derby!

1610
02:09:45,477 --> 02:09:49,439
或者僅僅去放風箏！這只有潑平斯知道！
Or I might just fly a kite! Only Poppins would know!

1611
02:09:49,689 --> 02:09:53,608
潑平斯？ 我的保姆。那首荒謬的歌就是她唱的。
Poppins?
My nanny. She's the one who sings that ridiculous song.

1612
02:09:53,860 --> 02:09:58,113
一湯匙糖讓苦藥服下
A spoonful of sugar makes the medicine go down

1613
02:09:58,364 --> 02:10:00,115
甜藥好入口
The medicine go down

1614
02:10:00,366 --> 02:10:04,369
甜藥好入口……
The medicine go down The medicine...

1615
02:10:05,537 --> 02:10:08,247
像三月裏的野兔般瘋狂
Mad as a March hare.

1616
02:10:08,498 --> 02:10:13,043
一隻叫史密斯的木假腿
A wooden leg named Smith.

1617
02:10:13,712 --> 02:10:19,007
史密斯有條木假腿
A wooden leg named Smith.

1618
02:10:19,508 --> 02:10:23,385
木假腿……
A wooden le...

1619
02:10:35,357 --> 02:10:38,525
父親？父親！
Father? Father!

1620
02:10:38,777 --> 02:10:40,612
父親，下來！
Father, come down!

1621
02:10:40,862 --> 02:10:46,449
爸爸，爸爸！回來！
Daddy! Daddy, come back!

1622
02:10:53,916 --> 02:10:59,545
風向轉變了，非常精確地從西邊刮來！
Wind's come around, blowing dead on from the west!

1623
02:11:00,423 --> 02:11:02,466
她不關心我們身上發生的事情
She doesn't care what happens to us.

1624
02:11:02,716 --> 02:11:07,803
她只答應呆到風向轉變為止。是吧，瑪麗?潑平斯？
She only promised to stay till the wind changed. Isn't that right, Mary Poppins?

1625
02:11:08,053 --> 02:11:12,557
請把衣帽架遞過來好嗎？
Will you bring me my hat stand, please?

1626
02:11:13,225 --> 02:11:18,646
瑪麗?潑平斯，你不愛我們了嗎？
Mary Poppins, don't you love us?

1627
02:11:19,315 --> 02:11:21,941
不關心我們的遭遇了嗎？
And what would happen to me
may I ask...

1628
02:11:22,193 --> 02:11:27,237
請問如果我愛所有的小孩，我該給誰告別呢？
if I loved all the children I said goodbye to?

1629
02:11:28,656 --> 02:11:31,491
是的，先生，沒錯。喬治 W 班克斯
Yes, sir, that's right. George W. Banks.

1630
02:11:31,744 --> 02:11:33,995
櫻桃樹大街17號
17 Cherry Tree Lane.

1631
02:11:34,245 --> 02:11:36,455
大約6英尺高，是的。
About six foot one, I'd say, sir.

1632
02:11:36,706 --> 02:11:39,999
是的，今天早上第一件事情就是給他工作的銀行打了電話
Oh, yes, we rang up his bank first thing this morning.

1633
02:11:40,251 --> 02:11:44,003
目前我們所知道的唯一事情就是，他昨晚就已經離開了
The only thing we discovered was, he'd been discharged last night.

1634
02:11:44,255 --> 02:11:47,257
他很沮喪，沒說要幹什麼
No telling what he might do in a fit of despondency.

1635
02:11:47,508 --> 02:11:49,343
不會去投河吧？
Wouldn't hurt to have them drag the river.

1636
02:11:49,593 --> 02:11:53,470
在薩克福橋附近有一個非常合適的地點，因投河自盡而聞名
There's a nice spot there by Suffolk Bridge. Popular with jumpers.

1637
02:11:53,723 --> 02:11:56,266
真的，艾倫！
Really, Ellen!

1638
02:11:56,516 --> 02:11:59,518
他看上去還不錯，很鎮定，先生
He seemed to have been a fine, stable gentleman, sir.

1639
02:11:59,770 --> 02:12:02,688
沒有陰謀，如果你知道我的意思。
No hanky-panky, if you know what I mean.

1640
02:12:02,939 --> 02:12:06,192
呃，日常習慣嘛。幾乎沒有人知道 甜藥好入口
Oh, regular habits, sir. Well, far as anyone knows.
The medicine go down

1641
02:12:06,443 --> 02:12:08,443
甜藥好入口
The medicine go down

1642
02:12:08,694 --> 02:12:11,112
只要一湯匙糖 是他！
Just a spoonful of sugar
It's him!

1643
02:12:11,363 --> 02:12:13,406
幫你把苦藥…… 或者聲音聽起來像是他
Helps the medicine
Or something that sounds like him.

1644
02:12:13,657 --> 02:12:15,532
服下 班克斯夫人，能不能讓房子裏的人小聲一點
Go down
Mrs Banks, could we have a little less noise...

1645
02:12:15,786 --> 02:12:20,623
我聽不到警長的聲音了 他現在很興奮
on the premises? I can't make out what the inspector's sayin'.
In the most delightful way

1646
02:12:20,873 --> 02:12:23,208
只要一湯匙糖
Just a spoonful of sugar

1647
02:12:23,459 --> 02:12:26,794
讓苦藥服下 喬治！
Makes the medicine go down
George!

1648
02:12:27,046 --> 02:12:29,338
哦，喬治，你沒有去投河
Oh, George, you didn't jump in the river.

1649
02:12:29,589 --> 02:12:31,589
你真明智啊
How sensible of you.

1650
02:12:31,841 --> 02:12:35,052
好了，先生，找到他了！
It's all right, sir. He's been found!

1651
02:12:35,303 --> 02:12:37,221
不，還活著！
No, alive!

1652
02:12:37,472 --> 02:12:41,349
或者我以為。他正在親吻班克斯夫人
Or so I presume. He's a-kissin' a-Mrs. Banks.

1653
02:12:41,600 --> 02:12:43,726
我真的很擔心，在銀行發生了什麼事情？
I've been so worried. What happened at the bank?

1654
02:12:43,978 --> 02:12:46,730
我被解雇了，趕了出來，扔到了大街上
I've been sacked, discharged, flung into the street.

1655
02:12:46,981 --> 02:12:51,234
一湯匙糖能讓苦藥服下
A spoonful of sugar makes the medicine go down

1656
02:12:51,485 --> 02:12:54,904
他剛才的行為有點不正常
Gone off his crumpet. That's what he's done.

1657
02:12:55,155 --> 02:12:58,157
甜藥好入口 瘋瘋癲癲的
The medicine go down
Dotty as you please.

1658
02:12:58,408 --> 02:13:01,576
喬治，你在地下室到底在做什麼？
George, what on earth were you doing in the cellar?

1659
02:13:01,827 --> 02:13:05,538
一會兒你就知道了。孩子們在哪裏？簡？邁克爾？
You'll see in a moment. Where are the children? Jane? Michael?

1660
02:13:05,790 --> 02:13:08,957
你們的父親在叫。 聽起來不像是父親的聲音
Your father's calling you.
It doesn't sound like Father.

1661
02:13:09,211 --> 02:13:14,465
簡？邁克爾？ 快跑去吧
Jane? Michael?
Run along. Spit spot!

1662
02:13:18,092 --> 02:13:21,053
你不會走吧，瑪麗?潑平斯？
You won't go, Mary Poppins, will you?

1663
02:13:21,304 --> 02:13:25,516
快！快！
Spit spot.

1664
02:13:33,691 --> 02:13:37,486
他修好了！
He mended it!

1665
02:13:40,823 --> 02:13:44,283
太好了！ 你怎麼修的？
It's wonderful!
However did you manage it?

1666
02:13:44,534 --> 02:13:47,495
花兩便士買了紙和繩子
With tuppence for paper and strings

1667
02:13:47,745 --> 02:13:50,789
雙腳站在地上
You can have your own set of wings

1668
02:13:51,040 --> 02:13:56,252
你可以讓風箏擁有自己的翅膀 緊緊抓住繩子
With your feet on the ground
You're a bird in flight

1669
02:13:56,504 --> 02:13:59,964
你就能像鳥兒一樣飛翔
With your fist holding tight

1670
02:14:00,216 --> 02:14:02,258
來放飛你的風箏吧
To the string of your kite

1671
02:14:02,510 --> 02:14:04,969
吼，吼，吼
Oh, oh, oh

1672
02:14:05,220 --> 02:14:08,513
讓我們去放風箏
Let's go fly a kite

1673
